room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Escape Rhode Island in Providence
room_description: The klaxon wails in the empty woodland surrounding Missile Battery PR-79. Tonight is the night the crew has been preparing for… one final launch test before the base goes fully operational at 0600. You know something isn’t quite right, but it is too late push the test off now. Does your crew have what it takes to complete your mission?
